OL,5, The world's oil and gas industry has   
OL,6, been warned it faces a "moment of      
OL,7, truth" at next week's key UN climate   
OL,8, conference.                            
OL,10,FDr Fatih Birol was speaking as global  
OL,11,Fenergy watchdog the IEA issued a new   
OL,12,Freport on the future of fossil fuels.  
OL,14,FHe said the sector must choose between 
OL,15,Fcontributing to the climate crisis or  
OL,16,F"becoming part of the solution".       
OL,18,FLast year fossil fuel companies were   
OL,19,Fresponsible for just 1% of global      
OL,20,Finvestment in renewable energy.        
